snippet.textDisplay:
1:24 you can see all the musicians setting up for the song, and then Kaavish walks by Hannan towards them. Hannan walks away depressed, and I don't think he intended to stay in that area, but I think the old lady giving him the flower makes him sit down for a moment. Then he listens. And the words of Jaffer do have an effect on him, as we hear him hum the same tune at the end. 

BEAUTIFUL STORYTELLING
